vec2 raySphereIntersect(vec3 r0, vec3 rd, vec3 s0, float sr) {
    float t = dot(s0 - r0, rd);
    vec3 t_point = r0 + t*rd;
    float y = length(s0-t_point);

    if(y<sr){
        float x = sqrt(sr*sr - y*y);
        float t1 = t-x;
        float t2 = t+x;
        return vec2(t1, t2);
    }

    return vec2(-42.);
}

float [25] eval_sh_bases_c(vec3 dir_vec){    
    float x = dir_vec[0];
    float y = dir_vec[1];
    float z = dir_vec[2];
    float xx = x * x;
    float yy = y * y;
    float zz = z * z;
    float xy = x * y;
    float yz = y * z;
    float xz = x * z;
    float [25] res;

    res[0] = SH_C0;
    res[1] = -SH_C1 * y;
    res[2] = SH_C1 * z;
    res[3] = -SH_C1 * x;

    res[4] = SH_C2[0] * xy;
    res[5] = SH_C2[1] * yz;
    res[6] = SH_C2[2] * (2.0 * zz - xx - yy);
    res[7] = SH_C2[3] * xz;
    res[8] = SH_C2[4] * (xx - yy);

    res[9] = SH_C3[0] * y * (3. * xx - yy);
    res[10] = SH_C3[1] * xy * z;
    res[11] = SH_C3[2] * y * (4. * zz - xx - yy);
    res[12] = SH_C3[3] * z * (2. * zz - 3. * xx - 3. * yy);
    res[13] = SH_C3[4] * x * (4. * zz - xx - yy);
    res[14] = SH_C3[5] * z * (xx - yy);
    res[15] = SH_C3[6] * x * (xx - 3. * yy);

    res[16] = SH_C4[0] * xy * (xx - yy);
    res[17] = SH_C4[1] * yz * (3. * xx - yy);
    res[18] = SH_C4[2] * xy * (7. * zz - 1.);
    res[19] = SH_C4[3] * yz * (7. * zz - 3.);
    res[20] = SH_C4[4] * (zz * (35. * zz - 30.) + 3.);
    res[21] = SH_C4[5] * xz * (7. * zz - 3.);
    res[22] = SH_C4[6] * (xx - yy) * (7. * zz - 1.);
    res[23] = SH_C4[7] * xz * (xx - 3. * yy);
    res[24] = SH_C4[8] * (xx * (xx - 3. * yy) - yy * (3. * xx - yy));

    return res;
}

vec4 softwareBilinear(sampler2D tex, vec2 uv)
{
    ivec2 int_texSize = textureSize( tex, 0 );
    vec2 texSize = vec2(float(int_texSize.x), float(int_texSize.y));

    vec2 pos = uv * texSize - 0.5;
    vec2 f = fract(pos);

    vec2 pos_top_left = floor(pos);

    // we are sample center, so it's the same as point sample
    vec4 tl = texture(tex, (pos_top_left + vec2(0.5, 0.5)) / texSize, -100.0);
    vec4 tr = texture(tex, (pos_top_left + vec2(1.5, 0.5)) / texSize, -100.0);
    vec4 bl = texture(tex, (pos_top_left + vec2(0.5, 1.5)) / texSize, -100.0);
    vec4 br = texture(tex, (pos_top_left + vec2(1.5, 1.5)) / texSize, -100.0);

    vec4 ret = mix(mix(tl, tr, f.x), mix(bl, br, f.x), f.y);

    return ret;
}

vec4 get_texture_map(sampler2D texture_map, vec2 uv){
    vec4 coords = texture(texture_map, vec2(uv.x, 1.-uv.y)) * texture_max + texture_min;// min max to dequantize texture
    return coords;
}

float norm(vec3 v)
{
    return (sqrt(v[0] * v[0]
    + v[1] * v[1]
    + v[2] * v[2]));
}

    return x;

if(x > 1.)
    return 1.;

float[64] dick_bilinear_sample_tri_plane(vec3 tex_coords, sampler2D xy_texture, sampler2D xz_texture, sampler2D yz_texture){
    float[64] result;

    vec2 xy = vec2(tex_coords.x, tex_coords.y) * .5 + .5;
    vec2 xz = vec2(tex_coords.x, tex_coords.z) * .5 + .5;
    vec2 yz = vec2(tex_coords.y, tex_coords.z) * .5 + .5;

    for(float i=0.; i<16.; i = i + 1.){
        vec4 xy_f = get_texture_map(iChannel0, vec2((xy.x/16.) + (i / 16.), xy.y));
        vec4 xz_f = get_texture_map(iChannel1, vec2((xz.x/16.) + (i / 16.), xz.y));
        vec4 yz_f = get_texture_map(iChannel2, vec2((yz.x/16.) + (i / 16.), yz.y));

        vec4 i_res = xy_f + xz_f + yz_f;

        int int_i = int(i);

        result[int_i*4] = clamp_relu(i_res[0]); 
        result[int_i*4 + 1] = clamp_relu(i_res[1]);
        result[int_i*4 + 2] = clamp_relu(i_res[2]);
        result[int_i*4 + 3] = clamp_relu(i_res[3]);
    }

    return result;
}

float[89] concat_basis_features(float[25] basis, float[64] point_features){
    float[89] result;
    for(int i=0; i<64; i++){
        result[i] = point_features[i];
        if(i<25){
            result[64+i] = basis[i];
        }
    }
    return result;
}

void mainImage( out vec4 fragColor, in vec2 fragCoord )
{
    vec2 uv =  fragCoord.xy / iResolution.xy; // 0 <> 1
    uv.y = 1. - uv.y;
    uv -= .5;
    uv.x *= iResolution.x / iResolution.y;
    uv *= 2.;
    //get ro, rd:

    float time = iTime / 4.;

    // cos(time)*.5
    vec3 ro = vec3(sin(time*.5), 0., cos(time*.5)* -1. + sin(time*.5) * .5);
     ro *= .5;
//    vec3 ro = vec3(0.,0.,-1.);
    vec3 lookat = vec3(0.);

    float zoom = 1.;

    vec3 f = normalize(lookat-ro);
    vec3 r = normalize(cross(vec3(0., 1., 0.), f));
    vec3 u = cross(f, r);

    vec3 c = ro + f*zoom;
    vec3 i = c + uv.x*r + uv.y*u;
    vec3 rd = i-ro;

    //end

    //Get ray params:
    vec2 t = raySphereIntersect(ro, rd, vec3(0., 0., 0.), SPHERE_RADIUS);
    if(t == vec2(-42.)){
        fragColor = vec4(0., 0., 0., 1.);
        return;
    }

    vec3 t0 = ro + rd * t[0];
    vec3 t1 = ro + rd * t[1];

    t0 /= SPHERE_RADIUS;
    t1 /= SPHERE_RADIUS;

    // t0 = normalize(t0);
    // t1 = normalize(t1);

    float d = norm(t0 - t1);
    //end

    float[25] sh_basis = eval_sh_bases_c(rd);

    vec3 d0 = rd*0.5;
    vec3 input_coords = t0;

    float[64] m_pointfeatures = dick_bilinear_sample_tri_plane(input_coords, xy_texture, xz_texture, yz_texture);

    float[89] concated_feats = concat_basis_features(sh_basis, m_pointfeatures);

    vec4 dist = light_field(concated_feats);

    if(dist[3] > d){
        fragColor = vec4(0., 0., 0., 1.);
        return;
    }
    fragColor = dist;
    for(int i=0; i<2; i++){
        input_coords = input_coords + d0 * dist[3];
         m_pointfeatures = dick_bilinear_sample_tri_plane(input_coords, xy_texture, xz_texture, yz_texture);
         concated_feats = concat_basis_features(sh_basis, m_pointfeatures);
         dist = light_field(concated_feats);
         if(dist[3] > d){
            fragColor = vec4(0., 0., 0., 1.);
             return;
         }
     }

    if(dist[3] > d){
         fragColor = vec4(0., 0., 0., 1.);
         return;
    }


    vec3 targetcoords = input_coords + d0 * dist[3];
    float[64] t_pointfeatures = dick_bilinear_sample_tri_plane(targetcoords, xy_texture, xz_texture, yz_texture);
    concated_feats = concat_basis_features(sh_basis, t_pointfeatures);
    vec4 color = light_field(concated_feats);

    fragColor = vec4(color.rgb,1.);
}
